snippet.title: Arcade Game: Changes (1982 Orca)
snippet.description:
A maze game just like pac-man where you controls a caterpillar that crawls along the branches of a maze-like tree eating nuts and strawberries while avoiding deadly bugs and a hungry bird. The caterpillar changes into a butterfly after everything has been eaten.

Note: Cheats were used. The game has 100 levels and it's endless. I killed myself afterwards when levels start repeating and after all levels are shown
